# maru
Contains an assignment for AI & ML course (implement AI & ML algorithm from scratch) and solving some data
science challenges.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisite

1. Install `Python 3.x` and `Anaconda 2018.12`.
2. Install `R 3.4.4`.
